Class XMLMarschallingException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • xml.XMLMarschallingException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class XMLMarschallingException
extends java.lang.Exception
    This Exception is thrown whenever there is an error while creating the XML file from the requirement analysis class. This Exception is an addition to the JAXBException and covers all errors that are now caught in the JAXBException.
